{"tid":513391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［老麥改經營模式事件］香港人比少少骨氣好冇","createTime":"2017-12-29T12:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T07:04:32.000Z","uid":57638,"like":409,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e82ee7143c756dbd8e98554db822616887dee1","tid":513391,"uid":57638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"單一件福喜雞事件已經睇得出香港人同日本人分別幾大<br />\n日本人就團結一心，抵制老麥<br />\n香港人就逆來順受，多多幫襯<br />\n<br />\n平時鐸叔突登比少薯條、紙巾、醬汁都不在話下，而家連全翼都唔比嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你一個雞翼餐實際成本唔洗10蚊，但你就收成30幾，真係堪稱最無良心企業<br />\n<br />\n我由呢刻起唔會再食老麥，希望所有覺得自己受到影響既人都可以坐言起行罷食，而唔係一邊屌一邊幫襯，日本人可以令到老麥跪低，點解我地唔可以？"},{"pid":"fa1ffbc954fa1d86d22bcfc51456733fae5bea4a","tid":513391,"uid":21139,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"戒左老麥3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c734038e00c0dce4213dcc7017d1be1cf235997e","tid":513391,"uid":131122,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"fa1ffbc954fa1d86d22bcfc51456733fae5bea4a","tid":513391,"uid":21139,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"戒左老麥3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"我一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61173ee25d5d54714e9706b69cc24b86300c4f75","tid":513391,"uid":38539,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"咁都要其他食肆爭氣至得架<br />\n價就識加 野食就越嚟越難食"},{"pid":"21e12d1d2c90d8e64c6e649b22ee472973360ac7","tid":513391,"uid":49004,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"任何野&ldquo;回歸&rdquo;中國都會變垃圾"},{"pid":"e0ee8c1f6ff6ce0ec0aa37b101498ede5f4da42b","tid":513391,"uid":21139,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戒左老麥3年<im